The name of the ["Tale"] world, a portmanteau of Die and Gaea.  Dya is a cube ominously analogous to a die. (Make your own cube with this [https://cixar.com/tale/art/world/cutout.png cutout]!)

||<:tableclass="frame">https://cixar.com/tale/art/world/all-700.png||

The world has six faces:

 * ["Euia"]
 * ["Occia"]
 * ["Borea"]
 * ["Austra"]
 * ["Oria"]
 * ["Dysia"]

Inflections:
 * ["Dyan"]  - a person of ["Dya"]
 * ["Dyal"] - of or pertaining to ["Dya"]
 * ["Dyo"] - the bard that weaves the ["Tale"] of ["Dya"]
 * ["PrincessDya"] - regent of ["Euia"] in ["U"]


